<section id="faq-page">
  <header class="page-header">
    <h1 class="yellow-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
    <p>Here are answers to some common questions about the platform, courses, and instructors.</p>
  </header>

  <section class="faq-list" aria-labelledby="faq-heading">
    <h2 id="faq-heading" class="visually-hidden">Frequently Asked Questions List</h2>

    <article class="faq-item">
      <h3>How do I register for a course?</h3>
      <p>Go to the Courses page and click on the course you're interested in. From there, you'll find instructions to register.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="faq-item">
      <h3>Can I attend live sessions later?</h3>
      <p>Yes, all live sessions are recorded and made available to registered learners after the session.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="faq-item">
      <h3>How can I contact an instructor?</h3>
      <p>Visit the Instructors page and use the provided contact details or contact form if available.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="faq-item">
      <h3>Is there a cost to participate?</h3>
      <p>Most courses and events are free. Some special programs may require registration fees, which will be clearly stated.</p>
    </article>
  </section>
</section>

